ASSIGNMENT:
===========

-> write an program to print 1 to 10 using for loop.



Example:
========


public class Count {

	public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {

		for (int i = 1; i <= 10; i++) {

			System.out.println(i);
		}

	}

}




